    "name": "Seasons of Solitude",
    "steam_appid": 3312670,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对长老的试炼</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Seasons of Solitude》是一款以爱沙尼亚自然与神话为灵感、设定在史前世界的回合制生存策略游戏。你被放逐，分裂为两个自我：流放者（Exile）与其回响（Echo）。唯有携手前行，读懂土地、规划路线，才能在四季更替中维持脆弱的平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划未知</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场试炼都从陌生的土地开始。规划意味着了解每一格地块能提供什么、何时收集、何时放手以减轻土地负担。站位得当可引发强力连击，奖励高效的土地利用。将地块转化为新状态，让你的痕迹留在世界上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/ae273fbf39ca095ba41082de40c5c968.poster.avif?t=1769079398\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/ae273fbf39ca095ba41082de40c5c968.webm?t=1769079398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/ae273fbf39ca095ba41082de40c5c968.mp4?t=1769079398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有目的地收集</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食物、水和材料从不保证。地块会枯竭并以新形式回归，让你理解土地循环。若过度索取，地块会退化成贫瘠草地，降低产出并拖累区域。修复疲惫的土地才能维持循环。四季带来额外压力，限制能采集的资源及其时机。生存意味着在维系生命、提升工具与保护土地之间取得平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/b1d8c3cdd4a9b42e12632da90a56bd31.poster.avif?t=1769079398\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/b1d8c3cdd4a9b42e12632da90a56bd31.webm?t=1769079398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/b1d8c3cdd4a9b42e12632da90a56bd31.mp4?t=1769079398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>守护你的收获</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你辛苦获得的资源从不安全。动物会夺取它们需要的食物与水，甚至吞噬你努力培育之物。若过度阻止，它们会饿死并留下枯竭的地块。危险会落在挣扎中的区域，阻断通路，却也可借助工具开启新的互动方式。守护重要之物，让必要之物流动，并决定你愿意牺牲什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/7cdb64584fbae3601fd20401c794d3c4.poster.avif?t=1769079398\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/7cdb64584fbae3601fd20401c794d3c4.webm?t=1769079398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/7cdb64584fbae3601fd20401c794d3c4.mp4?t=1769079398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>适应与进化</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大地从不静止。区域会因你的使用方式改变规模与强度。扩张区域以求更大奖励，或保持其规模以降低风险。孤立区域虽能繁荣，但若被忽视便会迅速崩溃。每个区域都会影响全局，使世界的韧性提升或衰退。工具将重塑你的策略：修复贫土、跳过更新周期、将材料转化为土地令牌、捕捉过度活跃的野兽充作食物，或利用灾害获取稀有资源。季节加压、危机加剧，你的生存取决于你如何读懂土地并由此制定计划。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/344f3c806dbc63d3cb907a5b2c64c1eb.poster.avif?t=1769079398\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/344f3c806dbc63d3cb907a5b2c64c1eb.webm?t=1769079398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312670/extras/344f3c806dbc63d3cb907a5b2c64c1eb.mp4?t=1769079398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每场试炼皆为精心设计</strong> <br>每张地图都是独立的生存挑战。关卡非程序生成，但不断变化的环境、危险与工具解锁，使其可重复游玩并拥有多种可行策略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>季节将反击</strong> <br>夏养你，秋令你挨饿。沼泽拖慢脚步，寒霜封锁道路，干旱夺走水源。每一次变化都迫使你重新规划。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存之器</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在试炼中解锁工具，获得新的生存行动。每件工具都会改变你的选择，开辟新路径，并以独特方式对抗威胁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大地会回应</strong> <br>世界由多个区域组成，会追踪你的采集方式。悉心照料便能更新、提高产出；过度索取则会枯萎，增加危险并削弱周围。局部变化会影响全局，改变更新概率，塑造旅途基调。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>值得坚守的世界</strong> <br>手绘地块灵感来自爱沙尼亚的自然与神话。每一块地都很美，每一步都很危险。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>孤独试炼你的极限</strong> <br>无部族，无第二次机会。唯有你的选择决定能否生存。探索、适应、坚持，长老正注视着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
